## Common Port Ranges

### Default Scan
```bash
nmap 10.10.10.10
```
- Scans **top 1000 most common ports**

### Specific Ports
```bash
nmap -p 80,443 10.10.10.10          # Scan ports 80 and 443
nmap -p 1-100 10.10.10.10           # Scan ports 1-100
nmap -p- 10.10.10.10                # Scan ALL 65535 ports
```

### Port Ranges
```bash
nmap -p 20-25,80,443,3000-4000 10.10.10.10
```

